casebody.data:
Vacated and Remanded on Appeal

No. 73-1413. Staats, Comptroller General, et al. v. American Civil Liberties Union, Inc., et al.

Appeal from D. C. D. C. [Probable jurisdiction noted, 417 *1031U. S. 944.] Judgment vacated and case remanded with directions to dismiss the cause as moot. Mr. Justice Douglas took no part in the consideration or decision of this case. Reported below: 366 F. Supp. 1041.
